title: Ten Must Have Essential Reggae Albums [-emidius-]
description:
The included are considered by many to be some of the top essential Reggae albums of all time. Regardless of any album rankings...these are truly MUST OWN albums for anyone interested in Reggae. I hope you enjoy this collection and I will be releasing further collections in the near future.

1. Bob Marley & The Wailers - Legend


2. Desmond Dekker - Israelites


3. Jimmy Cliff The Harder They Come


4. Bob Marley - Catch A Fire


5. Peter Tosh - Legalize It


6. Toots & The Maytals - Funky Kingston


7. Lee Scratch Perry - Super Ape


8. Don Dada - Super Cat


9. The Skatalites - Guns Of Navarone


10. Shabba Ranks - As Raw As Ever
